name: AwesomeDonna
0:
”Alexa, ask Awesome Donna do you like Harvey?”
”Are you awesome?”
”Do you remember when we went to Paris?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: awesome donna
des: Hi, I'm the Donna and I'm awesome! Let's chat but don't be too sassy. People say I'm pretty witty. Sometimes I have ice cream... or a can opener. You can ask me who built me, what I think about Harvey, or if I remember when we went to Paris. Have fun and look me up if you get confused!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
